Package gr.aueb.cf.ch12.exercises.exe2.backapp.model

Class Holder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gr.aueb.cf.ch12.exercises.exe2.backapp.model.Holder
  • public final class Holder
extends java.lang.Object
    The Holder class represents an entity that holds information about an individual. It encapsulates the essential details such as ID, first name, last name, and social security number (SSN).
